title: #141: Do the  D.E.W with Rachel Wolfson
description:
Thank you for tuning In for another episode of Tin Foil Hat With Sam Tripoli! This episode we welcome our guest, funny comic Rachel Wolfson , to discuss Direct Energy Weapons and what we think caused this insane California fires.
Please check out my special "Sam Tripoli Live From The Viper Zoom: Zero Fucks" which drops Friday Nov 16th! on Vimeo.com!
